section.title: Catchment Data
section.para: Catchment data will be the focus of this section. High important issues should include DEM from the viewpoint of information source, development, errors, etc. Land use mapping, particularly for urban areas, soil mapping, etc needs to be introduced and their relevance to design flood estimation highlighted.
